OL,3,CLeipzig: Two killed after car drives
OL,4,Cinto crowd of people
OL,6,FA driver ploughed into people in the
OL,7,Fcentre of the German city of Leipzig
OL,8,Fon Monday, leaving two people dead,
OL,9,Fpolice said.
OL,11,FA city spokesperson said that another
OL,12,Ftwo people were seriously injured,
OL,13,FGerman news agency dpa reported.
OL,15,FA statement posted on the Leipzig city
OL,16,Fwebsite said the car and its driver
OL,17,Fhad been stopped and no longer posed
OL,18,Fany danger.
