OL,3,CLeipzig: Two killed after car drives
OL,4,Cinto crowd of people
OL,6,FThe incident happened in the
OL,7,FGrimmaische Strasse, a street that
OL,8,Fleads into central Leipzig's shopping
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,FLeipzig is located southwest of Berlin
OL,12,Fand has more than 630,000 inhabitants,
OL,13,Fmaking it one of the biggest cities in
OL,14,Feastern Germany.
OL,16,FThis is a breaking news story, more to
OL,17,Ffollow...
